title: Welcome to My Portfolio
text:
About Me
Hello! I’m Merlin Urbanski, a passionate researcher and aspiring data scientist with a deep interest in predictive analytics, spatial data, and statistical modeling. I am currently pursuing my Master’s in Methodology and Statistics for Behavioral, Biomedical, and Social Sciences at Utrecht University. I like turtles!

What I Do

Predictive Analytics: Designing models to uncover insights and make accurate predictions from data.

Statistical Modeling: Leveraging R and Python to develop robust statistical solutions for challenging problems.

Data Imputation: Researching innovative ways to handle missing data and ensure model reliability.
